@startuml Sequence Diagram - Booking Process
!define TITLE Sequence Diagram - Room Booking Process
title TITLE

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #0066CC
skinparam actorBackgroundColor #FFE8E8

actor Tenant
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Booking Service" as BookingService
participant "Room Service" as RoomService
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Email Service" as Email

Tenant -> App: Search for available rooms
App -> Gateway: GET /rooms?city=X&dates=Y
Gateway -> RoomService: Query available rooms
RoomService -> DB: Fetch rooms
DB --> RoomService: Room list
RoomService --> Gateway: Available rooms
Gateway --> App: Room list
App --> Tenant: Display rooms

Tenant -> App: Select room & proceed to booking
App -> App: Validate dates & price
App -> Gateway: POST /bookings
Gateway -> BookingService: Create booking
BookingService -> RoomService: Verify room availability
RoomService -> DB: Check availability lock
DB --> RoomService: Available
BookingService -> DB: Create booking record (PENDING)
DB --> BookingService: Booking ID
BookingService --> Gateway: Booking created
Gateway --> App: Booking ID & payment details
App --> Tenant: Show payment form

Tenant -> App: Enter payment details
App -> App: Validate card info
App -> Gateway: POST /payments
Gateway -> PaymentService: Process payment
PaymentService -> PaymentService: Validate amount & currency
PaymentService -> PaymentService: Call payment gateway
PaymentService --> PaymentService: Payment confirmed
PaymentService -> DB: Create payment record (COMPLETED)
DB --> PaymentService: Payment saved
PaymentService -> BookingService: Update booking status
BookingService -> DB: Update booking (CONFIRMED)
DB --> BookingService: Updated
BookingService -> Email: Send confirmation
Email --> Tenant: Booking confirmation email
PaymentService --> Gateway: Payment success
Gateway --> App: Payment completed
App --> Tenant: Booking confirmed!

@enduml